1. *Odgovorim* na pitanje što je najvažnije u životu. (I answer the question of what is the most important thing in life.)
2. Oni očekuju da im *odgovorim* u roku od 24 sata. (They expect me to respond within 24 hours.)
3. Nisam siguran kako bih mu *odgovorio* na tu poruku. (I'm not sure how to respond to that message.)
4. Molim vas da mi *odgovorite* što prije. (Please respond to me as soon as possible.)
5. Ona nije ni pokušala *odgovoriti* na moje pitanje. (She didn't even try to answer my question.)
6. Kad bih znao kako *odgovoriti* na to pitanje, ne bih imao problema. (If I knew how to answer that question, I wouldn't have any problems.)
7. *Odgovori* koje sam dobio na intervjuu bili su vrlo korisni. (The answers I got in the interview were very helpful.)
8. Oni su *odgovorili* na pitanje bez ikakve okolišanja. (They answered the question without any hesitation.)
9. *Odgovorit ću* na tvoj e-mail kad budem imao više vremena. (I'll reply to your email when I have more time.)
10. Pitao sam je nekoliko puta, ali ona nije htjela *odgovoriti*. (I asked her several times, but she didn't want to answer.)